<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">أوز:</span> <span class="c2">(الْإِوَزَّةُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(الْإِوَزُّ)</span> بِكَسْرِ الْهَمْزَةِ فِيهِمَا الْبَطُّ وَقَدْ جَمَعُوهُ بِالْوَاوِ وَالنُّونِ فَقَالُوا: <span class="c2">(إِوَزُّونَ)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>